Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] He was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I couldn't blame him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:05.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[DOCTOR A yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:07.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD A yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:26.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's all he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[bell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm off, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But I'll be back real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And know that I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Everything is in honor of your memory, Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka's traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How many ways are there to stress this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:00.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your brother is not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, Sora already left to train for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] Yes. Don't fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's just sparring with Takeda today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[TAKEDA] Get up! --[SORAMARU] Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where might Tenka be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:55.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Takeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:24.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:37.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh. Sure is hard to have your world turn upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] His laugh... His technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Consider this a preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Death will be a sweet release for Tenka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're not getting near my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Those movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:04.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's uncanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] But I know how to counter Tenka's moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can take this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:33.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SUBORDINATE A] I see him! He's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I was expecting more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Someone worth my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Chutaro, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're safe at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,With us, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Takeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He managed to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:58.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That man could've easily killed us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So... why exactly are we still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] You're from the Army General Staff Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Name's Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We put you and your people in grave danger today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Your arrival probably saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you. That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're entitled to know what we're dealing with here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] A Kumou is no stranger to Orochi rumor and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He is an Orochi carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But, sir, we ourselves defeated the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not a vessel. An Orochi carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,While it is true that Orochi was slain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,intelligence confirms that the experiments have been resumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Orochi cells are integral to these trials,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,as you've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Carrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who would... do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Those responsible aren't priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You see... That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He is one of several test subjects running free right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My men have been ordered to capture them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We must minimize civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We'll have to terminate them otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If they're like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm equipped to help you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please. It would be my honor to aid you in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:39.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Records indicate you're a former Yamainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your offer. But I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] What? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Protocol demands it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My squad and I will see to this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Numerous factors bear consideration here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you suspicious of those within the ranks, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It pains me to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but current and former brass affiliations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,are not above suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The hell you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No Yamainu is capable of such treachery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly discount them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...once your former colleagues have been located, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Including our brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:19.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That man was looking for him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think he wants to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He hasn't sent us letters in a few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But... I'll do what I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I will protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You should trust Takeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:37.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He is one of us and I would trust him with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:40.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have no reason to suspect him or anyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I know that we can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] This is the location of the test facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you'll find something we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We've delayed our search long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please know, Takeda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My intention wasn't to insult the Yamainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I only wish to put this matter to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Soramaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This isn't without risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Somebody's gotta know where the other Yamainu are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Right. Heard from Takamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We haven't been training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He got in our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:43.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We know these people better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We have to focus. All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We can't let more suffer because of the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] Restless, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] I understand why, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:26.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But I don't advise moving forward too quickly on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your body needs proper time to heal itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I worry--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I have to do this, Nishiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I'm the vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please, sir. You have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I'm the only person alive that can possibly know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,what this guy's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If anyone can stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] No guards are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Something strong pried open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's a little unnerving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Nishiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If something happens, take Chutaro out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] He's more than capable of handling himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I can't risk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He'll be safest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:00.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't ask if I didn't trust you completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself as much as I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:09.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I won't fail you. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's an intense smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] They're... all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Hey... look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] An experiment log.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,April 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Applied the serum to test subject 84.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,April 10th. Appetite increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Body temp up two degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,May 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Scales started to appear on their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They weren't able to maintain composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fingers were amputated days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,September 27th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Serum administered six months prior to Number 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Still able to maintain composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:35.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Becoming aggressive, which is causing setbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He is becoming stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The entries end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That was days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:47.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] The other room had a cage for someone quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There are only remnants of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This Number 40 broke free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:54.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Massacring all in his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This is the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is it now, Takeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Aritomo Yamagata visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He reported the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yamagata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] He's a higher-up from the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Nishino clearly suspects top brass...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This might confirm his suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:24.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] No... Sosei... Abeno?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Yamainu were greatly opposed to the Orochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you truly willing to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:39.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We existed for the soul purpose of defeating it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Orochi cells are a different matter entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It stands to reason that they could prove beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they could even advance Japanese medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I will do anything to help. I'm in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It is a duty I will proudly uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:07.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No way. Sosei saw Tenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He knows all the hell and pain it brought
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,down on our brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TEST SUBJECT A yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[TAKEDA] Let me! --[SORAMARU] No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TEST SUBJECT A yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TEST SUBJECT A] Please... just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Make it stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It... hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:48.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can't... I'm so sorry... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] There are a lot of footprints at the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think they belong to the other escapees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:19.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] It's likely they're going to attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We have to catch them before anyone else gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I said come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Why didn't you tell me, Takamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:59.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tora. Miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kill anyone interesting or just blow off some steam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,by scaring the locals?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They weren't worth the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll try not to take that personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So much for gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to know if you're gonna be showing up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,bloody like the first time you came here is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It was dumb luck someone with a medical background
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,found you, Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep on nagging me and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The tough guy voice. I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Look, despite my better judgment, I just worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This Tenka Kumou guy isn't worth your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I just made 'em. Washing your hands wouldn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Eat up. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me hanging! Somebody cut me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--A trap. --Chutaro, I'm coming--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] What're you doing on my land?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't like trespassers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Make this easy for me and get to walkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Miss, are you responsible for this trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey... Have you seen anyone suspicious around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Anyone at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nope. Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] We mean you no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The man we're looking for is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You should stay indoors till he's found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Get gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ageha Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You were charged for murder and arson, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You'd been sentenced to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Take advantage of Gokumonjo's prison break last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well... Ain't this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I hadn't made an impression
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You weren't a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No, I was a jailer at Gokumonjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I think you're lying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] You again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You'll die! Just stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She was a doctor before Gokumonjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She might help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] He's... dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Those experiments tore up his insides.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He'll be lucky to live another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Or unlucky. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:38.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know you. You're all trying to capture Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's not really a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And he deserves to die free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:52.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] So this is one of the more successful subjects?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:55.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We received word he'd escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I knew he couldn't have gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:00.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Commander! Takamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Go on, Takamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No! You can't move him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:14.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We found what was left of the lab, Sosei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Both your names were in the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The man I know wouldn't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell me it isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Inukai... Master Shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All of you are together in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten the solemn oath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you made to destroy the Orochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] The Yamainu are no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do with Tora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,More experimentation, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:42.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's a great resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, Sosei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Remember Tenka's torment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember how I suffered because of what
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the Orochi did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How can you be a part of it, Sosei?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:18.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I got no business with you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just tell me where Tenka is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] And what business do you have with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His tissue cells were transplanted into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:27.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He did this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:32.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm not some bastard version of Tenka Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:34.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I will prove that I am the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:36.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eliminate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Because I know that I'm superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI] Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:48.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:50.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:51.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:55.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do try to stay out of our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:03.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Commander, wait a minute! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Consider yourself warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:07.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:22.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ever tell me any of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:26.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Am I the only Yamainu that's been left behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:27.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I have to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't just walk away from me, Takamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:35.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I'll be fine. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Takeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sosei. Is there news?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:07.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ashiya is apparently indisposed at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:09.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,However, he'll help if he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:31.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] His pulse is so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:39.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.07,0:24:40.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:42.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sis, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:43.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:45.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.55,0:24:47.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[DOCTOR A] You'll do no such thing, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:50.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why not worry about your own patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:52.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's my brother. I have to help him. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.99,0:24:54.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You are overstepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:55.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:07.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Malpractice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.64,0:25:10.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[DOCTOR A] So it would appear. Such a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:13.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have no one but yourself to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.61,0:25:17.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.78,0:25:19.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of your own flesh and blood, no less?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.78,0:25:21.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No one'll believe it wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.92,0:25:23.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's perfect, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:41.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.10,0:25:44.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:46.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:50.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You... saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.65,0:25:52.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:54.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The situation wasn't much different from when
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:56.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.18,0:25:58.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It hurts so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.69,0:26:02.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think we both know I'm not a doctor anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:04.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Still like to think you're my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.66,0:26:06.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We'll see this through together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.77,0:26:15.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.47,0:26:19.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Try to stay put for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.64,0:26:20.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:26.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.95,0:26:28.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If I'm lucky, it's the young'uns.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.02,0:26:31.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:33.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Those guys in black are seriously no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.56,0:26:41.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora wasn't the only one? Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.26,0:26:42.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[gunshots]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.63,0:26:47.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Targets have been neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.20,0:26:48.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're clear, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.82,0:27:05.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KITA] Ageha Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.09,0:27:08.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're one of the Gokumonjo escapees.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.06,0:27:10.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You were spotted with our primary target, Test Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.73,0:27:12.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Number 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.23,0:27:13.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell us where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.96,0:27:16.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And why the hell would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.03,0:27:19.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Our directive is to execute you on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.30,0:27:21.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Cooperate and we'll reconsider that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.84,0:27:27.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:28.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.01,0:27:30.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.08,0:27:37.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.02,0:27:44.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.86,0:27:47.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A Kumou defending a convicted felon?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.13,0:27:49.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This could be considered treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.33,0:27:52.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't think you're above consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.27,0:27:53.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am a Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.00,0:27:56.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Convict or not, I'm not turning a blind eye
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.90,0:27:59.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to someone being unjustly killed right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.91,0:28:02.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Fire, men! --But, sir--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.91,0:28:03.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:07.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KITA] Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:11.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Nishino!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.95,0:28:13.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.35,0:28:14.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think you can run?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.79,0:28:16.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.13,0:28:23.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.77,0:28:26.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.60,0:28:29.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They'll want to keep this attack contained...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.74,0:28:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. My men and I can hold them off
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.94,0:28:33.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.71,0:28:35.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I suggest you get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:36.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:40.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't trust him. He's military, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.38,0:28:41.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.95,0:28:46.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nishino... Yamainu are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.09,0:28:47.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.99,0:28:51.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know this is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.96,0:28:55.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And... I didn't want to be right about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.10,0:28:56.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You know what must be done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.27,0:29:00.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They have to be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.30,0:29:02.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Them and these damn experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.14,0:29:06.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[gunshots]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.78,0:29:10.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That was gunfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:13.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It seems the others are no longer our only concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.71,0:29:14.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:24.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.30,0:29:32.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you know your way around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.84,0:29:36.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.01,0:29:39.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.94,0:29:42.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't get you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:43.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.74,0:29:44.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You want Tora gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.88,0:29:47.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but you don't want the guys in black to take him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:50.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Seems we're on the same side here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.08,0:29:52.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So who is he to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.22,0:29:53.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Like a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.35,0:29:54.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.96,0:29:56.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.46,0:29:58.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We didn't know one another before this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.03,0:30:00.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No one knew Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.73,0:30:02.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't think he ever had anyone to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.43,0:30:07.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You do what you must to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.27,0:30:09.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Even if that means stealing or killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.17,0:30:14.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora saw the Orochi experiments as a way to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.98,0:30:16.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As a way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.95,0:30:23.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I found him barely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.08,0:30:25.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His health was pretty bad after his escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.92,0:30:27.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He was so torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.89,0:30:30.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't regret doing what I could to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.49,0:30:32.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How can you say that knowing what he's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:34.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:39.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So am I. I don't expect you to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.03,0:30:40.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But you didn't see him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.94,0:30:48.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Careful now. You know chewing wouldn't be the worst--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.44,0:30:55.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's good. It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:56.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.92,0:30:59.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You didn't see those tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.15,0:31:01.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You can't know what kind of life he had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.92,0:31:04.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.99,0:31:07.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can't ignore what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.09,0:31:09.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There are far too many lives at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.53,0:31:11.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly know what he's going through!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.90,0:31:14.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Tora is-- --[SORAMARU] But I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.97,0:31:16.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.40,0:31:18.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know his pain better than even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.47,0:31:19.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.11,0:31:24.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.89,0:31:33.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh. His endurance is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:36.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His stubborn will is likely what kept him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.06,0:31:38.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His resistance to the cells won't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.36,0:31:40.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.13,0:31:41.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Sosei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:44.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are you really planning to put him through more testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.44,0:31:49.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.31,0:31:56.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Inukai, Shi. Head to the facility now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.81,0:32:02.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru, please. You're too wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.45,0:32:06.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep Chutaro safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.45,0:32:07.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.83,0:32:14.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Finally using your teeth to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.00,0:32:18.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You don't have a chance against me, Takeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.20,0:32:24.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,"Even if you stand alone, don't hide your fangs."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.07,0:32:25.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You taught me that lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.61,0:32:26.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Takamine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.98,0:32:29.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.61,0:32:32.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.32,0:32:43.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was all that talk? Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.33,0:32:46.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:49.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your form is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.43,0:32:53.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.17,0:32:55.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why be any part of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:32:58.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I'll detain you, but I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.94,0:33:00.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're currently trying to obtain an item
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.57,0:33:04.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,capable of separating the Orochi from its host.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:07.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think death is the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.08,0:33:09.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well? You forget yourself so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.92,0:33:11.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Pride and strength make a Kumou.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.29,0:33:22.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.06,0:33:25.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make any sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.10,0:33:27.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You've protected this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.50,0:33:29.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You couldn't let me die!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.37,0:33:33.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You'd never treat someone this way no matter what they've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.21,0:33:35.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I forget how naÃ¯ve you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:38.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,In your way of thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.61,0:33:42.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,In your wielding of a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:44.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do not pick one up if you don't carry the resolve to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:46.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,when necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.05,0:33:47.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.09,0:33:51.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] Did you learn anything in all those years?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.63,0:33:54.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.50,0:33:59.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Kumou swords aren't for ending a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.43,0:34:01.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're for protecting people!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:03.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare discount me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.60,0:34:05.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am still a Yamainu!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.94,0:34:07.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm not naÃ¯ve.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:09.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A Kumou is what I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.99,0:34:20.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:35.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:38.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I deserve answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.61,0:34:40.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:50.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who has been giving you your information
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.35,0:34:51.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,on the experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.65,0:34:53.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sosei... You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.19,0:34:56.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're too stubborn to let this go...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.72,0:34:58.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Others will be even less sympathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:03.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's hard to imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.16,0:35:06.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We heard about the experiment from a guy with the army. His--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.34,0:35:15.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[SORAMARU] Sosei! --[TAKAMINE] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.64,0:35:17.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] So...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.58,0:35:21.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.28,0:35:23.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SUBORDINATE B] Number 40 is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.78,0:35:26.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,After him. Do not kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.19,0:35:27.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.19,0:35:35.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Oh, Abeno... Takamine...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.76,0:35:38.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your feigned interest in the Orochi experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.10,0:35:41.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,was so incredibly predictable. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.47,0:35:43.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why'd you shoot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:47.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[YAMAGATA] These two gentlemen will be aiding us
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.54,0:35:49.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,throughout the trials, Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:54.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Sir. You're aware they're Yamainu?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.11,0:35:57.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[YAMAGATA] Former. We couldn't ask for better help.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.25,0:36:00.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Their experience with Orochi is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.19,0:36:01.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's an honor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.56,0:36:06.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] I knew from that very moment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.63,0:36:09.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,that you were only going to screw things up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.73,0:36:11.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.47,0:36:13.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're behind all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.20,0:36:15.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Yamagata thought he was clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.37,0:36:17.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I will give him credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.10,0:36:21.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Employing a bunch of retired fools did force my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.14,0:36:22.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:26.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Money? Prestige? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.45,0:36:28.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Yes, all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.28,0:36:31.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But... most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.55,0:36:33.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...the extinction of Yamainu!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.79,0:36:36.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.32,0:36:40.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If only Yamagata truly understood how much I have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.13,0:36:43.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How much I've sacrificed for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.33,0:36:46.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The use of Orochi cells will save our great country!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.77,0:36:49.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why is it so impossible for Lord Yamagata
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:51.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to see any of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.64,0:37:02.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I do regret involving you in this, Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.22,0:37:05.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I needed someone without a previous personal affiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.22,0:37:07.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to kill the Yamainu squad...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.69,0:37:09.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.39,0:37:11.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You did give the Yamainu chase...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.63,0:37:13.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And it's clear you fought with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:15.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's a very reasonable assumption
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.40,0:37:18.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,that not a single soul survived such an intense battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.63,0:37:20.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Bastard! You planned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.47,0:37:22.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] I did warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.24,0:37:25.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You knew the risks. And proceeded to spite them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.28,0:37:32.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.25,0:37:37.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] I'd reconsider that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:39.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty fond of the people you're trying to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.29,0:37:40.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,there, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.56,0:37:44.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Tenka Kumou...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.36,0:37:49.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...has finally returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.46,0:37:50.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.60,0:37:51.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.93,0:37:55.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Damnit, Sosei.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.30,0:37:56.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:37:57.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.71,0:38:02.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] Do not let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.54,0:38:03.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fire freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.51,0:38:07.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Appears we've lost them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.88,0:38:09.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] What're you doing here, Tenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.48,0:38:11.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We can catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.32,0:38:12.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.62,0:38:15.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You always gotta be so difficult, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.26,0:38:16.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.46,0:38:18.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.40,0:38:23.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.43,0:38:24.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.83,0:38:28.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka? You're him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.44,0:38:29.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.60,0:38:31.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec. Where's Tora?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.61,0:38:34.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hopefully still with Master Shi and Inukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.81,0:38:36.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Probably being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.68,0:38:38.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.48,0:38:43.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Who's Tora?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.68,0:38:46.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He was one of the Orochi test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.65,0:38:48.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka... I have to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.86,0:38:51.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru... You're too injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.23,0:38:55.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey, little bro. Head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:38:57.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I got things handled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.30,0:38:58.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.43,0:39:00.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should be pushing yourself so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.63,0:39:02.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:04.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I've got four Yamainu for backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.57,0:39:09.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Too much for you, Takeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:11.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.31,0:39:12.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's just... the commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.95,0:39:14.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He just needs proper motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.02,0:39:16.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Wanna sit this one out?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.82,0:39:19.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Need to borrow my wheelchair, Sosei?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.02,0:39:21.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.79,0:39:25.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Run along.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.43,0:39:28.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Inukai and Shi need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.53,0:39:29.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.97,0:39:34.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your return is quite unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:36.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The funniest thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.50,0:39:39.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This geezer at a teahouse told me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.34,0:39:40.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:42.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kiiko's working for you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.58,0:39:44.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,and she was supposed to keep me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.61,0:39:51.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me... You know how stubborn he can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.39,0:39:53.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SUBORDINATE A] There they are! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.32,0:39:55.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm moving out front! Cover me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.86,0:39:57.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're not a commander anymore, Tenka!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.66,0:39:59.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[TENKA] Try to keep up! --Stop arguing, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.56,0:40:01.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] Don't test me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:03.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKAMINE] Takeda... Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.96,0:40:05.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TAKEDA] Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.04,0:40:10.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.07,0:40:11.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SUBORDINATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.71,0:40:13.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.07,0:40:15.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI] This is getting problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.75,0:40:21.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ashiya! I thought you couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.38,0:40:24.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASHIYA] I couldn't ignore the looming despair in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.55,0:40:25.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.81,0:40:46.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.01,0:40:51.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.75,0:40:53.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How are they doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.38,0:40:54.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.75,0:40:55.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where's the Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.95,0:40:58.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SHI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:15.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.90,0:41:47.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just how strong is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.93,0:41:49.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.91,0:41:59.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora. Why don't we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.08,0:42:01.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll whip you up some of those rice balls you love, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.47,0:42:21.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.91,0:42:35.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHINO] The experiment isn't over. He's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.19,0:42:40.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I got you. You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.06,0:42:44.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ageha.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.06,0:42:48.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[AGEHA] Now he remembers my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.76,0:42:50.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your timing is terrible, Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.03,0:42:55.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I thought this would be the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.17,0:42:57.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That I'd see you through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:01.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know you won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.84,0:43:05.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But helping you has meant everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.11,0:43:07.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.11,0:43:08.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,See ya real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.11,0:43:36.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.98,0:43:41.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.98,0:43:43.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:44.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.02,0:43:46.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No, Soramaru! You can't--!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:47.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.56,0:43:52.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.80,0:43:57.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.13,0:44:00.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.71,0:44:10.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] I am strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.28,0:44:11.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No one defeats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.88,0:44:15.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm the strongest. I'm invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.12,0:44:16.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.05,0:44:20.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.01,0:44:44.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] You want to help him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.04,0:44:48.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He wants to defeat him on his own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.25,0:44:51.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I would only interfere. So I wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.18,0:44:52.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] So you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.65,0:44:54.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.12,0:44:55.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.02,0:44:58.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I follow Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.16,0:45:01.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His wish is to do this alone and I will honor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.70,0:45:03.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.16,0:45:05.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO sighs] I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.73,0:45:07.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Then again, honoring someone's wish depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.77,0:45:09.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the true nature of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.37,0:45:10.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Of who commands it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.77,0:45:14.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nishiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.74,0:45:16.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who are you to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.38,0:45:19.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His ninja? Or something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.99,0:45:34.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.69,0:45:37.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.10,0:45:40.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His eyes turned black and his blood's gotta be boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.93,0:45:42.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.40,0:45:44.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.24,0:45:46.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yep. He's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.68,0:45:50.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.04,0:45:52.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soramaru... You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.98,0:45:55.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.95,0:46:04.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I understand. I see now!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.22,0:46:06.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] I am the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.04,0:46:22.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.17,0:46:49.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.00,0:46:52.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.87,0:46:55.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.71,0:46:58.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I remember what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.04,0:47:01.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I didn't honor my word, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.21,0:47:03.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't let you die, Soramaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.75,0:47:07.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.12,0:47:09.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.26,0:47:12.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I had to betray you to save you and I would do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.96,0:47:14.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.97,0:47:22.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.40,0:47:24.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He was pretty strong after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.08,0:47:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TORA] It doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.95,0:47:34.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.45,0:47:37.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What did I really accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.42,0:47:39.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was any of it worth a damn?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.89,0:47:44.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.23,0:47:49.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Ageha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.16,0:47:53.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey... I'm... hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.81,0:48:02.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sora! You okay, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.44,0:48:03.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.45,0:48:10.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.18,0:48:11.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.52,0:48:15.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.22,0:48:17.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If it'd been Tenka, maybe he'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.92,0:48:19.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He'd still be...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.06,0:48:22.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Hush up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.43,0:48:25.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done better, little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.03,0:48:27.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You did him a courtesy, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.30,0:48:29.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He got to die a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.51,0:48:35.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fighting held back the Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.88,0:48:38.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Focusing on his battle with you kept the beast at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.51,0:48:41.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.12,0:48:48.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You done good...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.56,0:48:50.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Real good, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.53,0:49:03.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[YAMAGATA] Excellent work, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.97,0:49:07.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A decision was finally reached for Nishino.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:09.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The war council will soon determine what's to be done
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.84,0:49:12.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,regarding others involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.41,0:49:15.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And what of the research facility, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.35,0:49:18.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It is dismantled entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.15,0:49:21.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Any cells, formulas, research, or what have you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.09,0:49:24.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,concerning the Orochi are no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.26,0:49:27.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.06,0:49:29.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have been a tremendous help, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.90,0:49:31.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Only wish I could've done more to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.60,0:49:34.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,this dreadful ordeal sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.17,0:49:36.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How are your associates and friends faring
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.17,0:49:37.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,in the aftermath?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.00,0:49:39.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is the Kumou boy on the mend?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.58,0:49:49.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Sora! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.88,0:49:51.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I could use some help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.65,0:49:53.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Okay! Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.39,0:50:04.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,"Wouldn't it be so great if everybody came over to eat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.20,0:50:07.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka has no consideration for those cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.20,0:50:08.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It will be a treat to have everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.64,0:50:11.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,under the same roof again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.30,0:50:13.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So... Find your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.54,0:50:18.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Nishiki? Who are you to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.05,0:50:23.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] His kindness overwhelms me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.42,0:50:31.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His upbringing was nothing like growing up Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.96,0:50:33.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.96,0:50:36.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Are the differences too big an obstacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.30,0:50:38.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Could you pack up and leave him behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.20,0:50:42.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] I don't think I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.97,0:50:44.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.54,0:50:47.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I long for something like a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.37,0:50:49.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want to be seen as more.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.51,0:50:52.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,More than just an unfledged of the Fuuma clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.01,0:50:54.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,More as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.72,0:51:00.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're so cute. I'd love to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.55,0:51:04.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I... Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.22,0:51:06.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored. We'll find your normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.29,0:51:09.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.63,0:51:10.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] You could've done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:12.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] I'm not a great multi-tasker.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.37,0:51:14.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Be careful carrying those.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.07,0:51:15.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.57,0:51:21.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You haven't recovered fully!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.04,0:51:21.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.91,0:51:24.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Moving around a little won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.41,0:51:25.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Man, this thing is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.41,0:51:27.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.65,0:51:30.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I went through the trouble of making that dish, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.30,0:51:44.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Get that away from my seat, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.06,0:51:45.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna grow up to be big and strong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.50,0:51:46.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,if you don't eat, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.53,0:51:49.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He makes his brothers do all the heavy lifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.07,0:51:51.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Tenka should really help since this was his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.35,0:52:04.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.62,0:52:05.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.75,0:52:09.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What are you doing all the way out here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.12,0:52:12.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Realized I never got a good look at the view
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.03,0:52:14.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.34,0:52:31.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] I figured I'd better do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.18,0:52:32.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SORAMARU] Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:34.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] I've got more of the world to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.31,0:52:36.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can't just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.08,0:52:37.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.65,0:52:38.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.75,0:52:40.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yamagata seems to think I baby you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.72,0:52:44.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,"It's time to let the boy prove himself as a man."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.33,0:52:48.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.66,0:52:50.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What does any of that even mean, Tenka?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.83,0:52:53.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried at all about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:55.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving it in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.80,0:52:57.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.18,0:53:05.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Just try not to doubt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.45,0:53:08.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You can do this, sweet little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.35,0:53:16.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[CHUTARO] Tenny! Tenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.72,0:53:19.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well, 15th Head...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.36,0:53:20.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Should we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.86,0:53:21.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
